reviews.reviewText: I use 1 cable to charger my phone and the other to charge my laptop and both seem to work just like the original cables that came with the product. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 29, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I’m writing my first product review in the hope that I save another shopper the hassle of buying these chargers. After maybe 5 charges they started acting up - only charging if you turned the cable a certain way, etc. Owned them for about 3 weeks and now neither will charge my phone regardless of how they’re positioned. Save your money and buy elsewhere.
